OL,5,Cpact'
OL,7,FA man from Devon who claimed he killed
OL,8,Fhis wife as part of a "suicide pact",
OL,9,Fhas been found guilty of her murder.
OL,11,FStephen Parsons, aged 71, was
OL,12,Fconvicted of killing 69-year-old Erica
OL,13,FParsons at their home in Bondleigh
OL,14,Flast year, following a two-week trial
OL,15,Fat Exeter Crown Court.
OL,17,FOn Friday 21 June, the judge sentenced
OL,18,FParsons to life in prison where he
OL,19,Fmust serve a minimum term of 13 years
OL,20,F- less the time already served.
