OL,7,FThe court heard that on 11 February
OL,8,F2023, police were called to the
OL,9,Fcouple's home after Stephen Parsons
OL,10,Fsent a message to a friend saying, "by
OL,11,Fthe time you read this we will be
OL,12,Fdead".
OL,14,FEmergency services rushed to the scene
OL,15,Fwhere they found Erica Parsons dead in
OL,16,Fbed.
OL,18,FStephen Parson was found next to her
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries to his arms and
OL,20,Fhe was taken to hospital for treatment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
