OL,7,FIn the ambulance, he was arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder and made comments
OL,9,Fto the officer about having caused
OL,10,FErica's death.
OL,12,FA postmortem examination of Erica's
OL,13,Fbody concluded that she had died from
OL,14,Fsuffocation between 9 and 10 February,
OL,15,Fat least 24 hours before Parsons
OL,16,Fsustained his injuries.
OL,18,FThe court heard evidence that in the
OL,19,Fmonths before the incident, the couple
OL,20,Fhad defaulted on numerous payments and
OL,21,Fhad growing debts.
