OL,7,FStephen Parsons had been telling
OL,8,Fcompanies they owed money to, that the
OL,9,Fcouple were both ill with cancer and
OL,10,Fwere undergoing treatment in hospital.
OL,12,FHe also claimed Erica had become
OL,13,Fdependent on drinking large quantities
OL,14,Fof alcohol on a weekly basis.
OL,16,FMedical evidence proved that these
OL,17,Fclaims were not true and neither had
OL,18,Fbeen undergoing treatment for cancer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
