OL,7,FParsons claimed that the couple, who
OL,8,Fwere well known for breeding Southern
OL,9,FPointer dogs, had made a pact to die
OL,10,Ftogether.
OL,12,FHowever, detectives found no evidence
OL,13,Fof this and were further able to show
OL,14,Fthrough the investigation that Erica
OL,15,Fhad been making plans for the future.
OL,17,FThis included going to dog shows and
OL,18,Fmeeting friends later that week.
