OL,7,FParsons pleaded guilty to manslaughter
OL,8,Fby diminished responsibility, claiming
OL,9,Fthat he had killed Erica as part of
OL,10,Fpact, but this was not accepted at an
OL,11,Fearlier hearing.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent James Dowler,
OL,14,FHead of the Major Crime Investigation
OL,15,FTeam said: "This was a sensitive and
OL,16,Fprolonged investigation.
OL,18,F"We welcome the verdict reached by the
OL,19,Fjury after hearing all the evidence
OL,20,Fand also the sentence passed by the
OL,21,Fjudge today.
