OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with Erica Parsons
OL,8,Fand all those who knew who her. Erica
OL,9,Floved animals and was heavily involved
OL,10,Fin the care of dogs and horses
OL,11,Fthroughout her life.
OL,13,F"I hope the outcome reached today
OL,14,Fprovides some closure to all those who
OL,15,Fhave been by her death."
